race.comment: SOMETHING FORJO (9) improved again winning a 60 at Gatton over this trip. That stacks right up for this and she maps for the run of the race. Is on a 9-day return and will get every chance to repeat the dose. MADALSA (3) was very plain here last time but won the two before easily at the track/trip. Has an inside gate and is a decent chance to bounce. SPRAY GUN (2) comes out of the same race beaten 2.2L racing forward. Has a 2kg claim today and the blinkers on again and he looks back on track. RINGER'S REWARD (6) has the rail and 2kg claim and is better than the form line suggests. Keep onside.
